                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-187-18621215 t18621215-187-punishment-75"></join>Confined Twelve Months</rs>.</hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">ADJOURNED TO MONDAY, JANURAY</hi> 5<hi rend="smallCaps">TH</hi>, 1863.</p>
